      "id": "PopularPost214733",
      "post_content": "Let's think of some cheap ass creatures to glomp a Lashwrithe onto:  \n  \n-[Child Of Night](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Child Of Night) or [Markov Patrician](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Markov Patrician): Both Lifelinky goodness!  \n  \n-[Vault Skirge](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vault Skirge),[Flensermite](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flensermite) or [Plague Stinger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plague Stinger): The moderating alternating trio of Flying, Infect and Lifelink; pick your choice!  \n  \n-[Reassembling Skeleton](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reassembling Skeleton): If the opponent doesn't have much artifact removal, this guy will stick around to cause some pain  \n  \n-[Tormented Soul](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tormented Soul): Have fun blocking that  \n  \n-[Mortis Dogs](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mortis Dogs)- Awkwardly the same CMC, but very funny!  \n  \n....why do I bother? Just slap it on your [Phyrexain Obliterator](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexain Obliterator)s and be on your way!",
      "posted_by": "Splizer",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost214733\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Let's think of some cheap ass creatures to glomp a Lashwrithe onto:<br/><br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Child Of Night\">Child Of Night</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Markov Patrician\">Markov Patrician</a>: Both Lifelinky goodness!<br/><br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Vault Skirge\">Vault Skirge</a>,<a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Flensermite\">Flensermite</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plague Stinger\">Plague Stinger</a>: The moderating alternating trio of Flying, Infect and Lifelink; pick your choice!<br/><br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reassembling Skeleton\">Reassembling Skeleton</a>: If the opponent doesn't have much artifact removal, this guy will stick around to cause some pain<br/><br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Tormented Soul\">Tormented Soul</a>: Have fun blocking that<br/><br/>-<a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Mortis Dogs\">Mortis Dogs</a>- Awkwardly the same CMC, but very funny!<br/><br/>....why do I bother? Just slap it on your <a class=\"autoCard\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Phyrexain Obliterator\">Phyrexain Obliterator</a>s and be on your way!</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\">\r\n            