      "id": "PopularPost156760",
      "post_content": "@infernox10:  \nI agree that it is a little contradictory but it helps fits the style of suicide monoblack which is basically win at any costs, even if those costs include physical or mental harm to yourself, your creatures, or anything else really..  \n  \nAlso, not strictly better than [Nightmare Lash](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Nightmare Lash) if you plan on using this in a non-black deck, Nightmare Lash is better (if you plan to use it with something like Overgrown Tomb or dual lands for example, lastly use with [Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth))",
